{
  "texts": [
    "As illustrated, the successful prediction made by AnnoPRO, NetGO3, PFmulDL or DeepGOPlus was indicated by a circle of light red, orange, light blue or light green, respectively, and AnnoPRO is the only one that reach > 90% accuracies in predicting MF families for both HSPs.",
    "Furthermore, there were 16 different MF families between HSPA1A and HSPA2 (highlighted by red frames in Additional file 1: Fig.",
    "S4 for HSPA1A and Additional file 1: Fig.",
    "S5 for HSPA2).",
    "As shown, AnnoPRO performed the best in most (13/16) families, while NetGO3, PFmulDL, DeepGOPlus successfully predicted 7, 10 and 3 families, respectively."
  ]
}